---
title: Crunchy Walnut Chicken with Asparagus  plus Mashed Potatoes & Lemon-Dijon Sauce
description: Crispy chicken and mustard are a perfect pairing. Our fresh take starts with chicken spread with mustard sauce and enveloped in a crunchy, nutty walnut-panko crust. Roast the chicken on a sheet pan alongside asparagus. Serve creamy mashed potatoes on the side, and top the asparagus with quick-pickled shallots just before serving for a bright bite.

